# URL of the authoritative Socket.IO server.
#
# - Local dev: leave unset (the client defaults to http://localhost:3000) or set
#   it to whatever PORT the server is on.
# - Production browser build: point at the VPS, e.g. https://escape.example.com
# - Capacitor / Android build: this MUST be set to the public VPS URL at build
#   time, because the value is baked into the bundle (the WebView has no
#   localhost server). Set it before running `npm run build`.
VITE_SERVER_URL=http://localhost:3000
